33
00:01:40,610 --> 00:01:43,950
If the virus is lucky enough to not be
cleared by the cilia.

34
00:01:43,950 --> 00:01:47,630
It may find a specific receptor on the
epithelial cell.

35
00:01:47,630 --> 00:01:49,350
These receptors determine whether or

36
00:01:49,350 --> 00:01:53,100
